  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286710/extras/ceddfd90e366c40465104b73af36fd0c.avif?t=1730391278\" width=534 height=210 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Softie is a short point and click game about a teddy bear looking for his owner. Explore a cozy, unassuming home, where an adorable plushie meets unexpected challenges. But don’t worry-teddy bears know nothing of fear!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play time around 30-40 minutes. ​</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>​</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Key features:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > ⚉​ Original Soundtrack</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > ⚉ ​Hand-drawn environment inspired by trinkets and toys of the early 2000's​</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > ⚉ Odd-ball characters to interact with</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286710/extras/ceddfd90e366c40465104b73af36fd0c.avif?t=1730391278\" width=534 height=210 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Softie is a short point and click game about a teddy bear looking for his owner. Explore a cozy, unassuming home, where an adorable plushie meets unexpected challenges. But don’t worry-teddy bears know nothing of fear!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play time around 30-40 minutes. ​</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>​</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Key features:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > ⚉​ Original Soundtrack</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > ⚉ ​Hand-drawn environment inspired by trinkets and toys of the early 2000's​</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > ⚉ Odd-ball characters to interact with</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
